{"type": "article", "id": 5910, "title": "Smaller Objects 家居饰品", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-05T07:54:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233821Q7oIz3t9LesqTC1g.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自斯德哥尔摩的设计事务所 Claesson Koivisto Rune 日前成立了一个新的家居品牌 Smaller Objects，并于本周的斯德哥尔摩家具展上发布了首批新品。其创始人 Mårten Claesson 表示：“当我们在市场上找不到我们想要的家居用品时，我们开始设计，这是一个充满激情的过程，就像业余爱好。”靠枕、花盆、杯垫、烛台等这些也许在家居环境中并不起眼的小物件，却传递出设计团队对日常物品的关注。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233818LGTyA9UvSleRcBh4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523381928SpIL0vmqNukDHC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233819SwMbP8G4EJs35y0g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233819YL8svBkwrW1aPiU5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233820yKPsj9mo0Q2R7zOB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}